"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-indonesias-first-olympic-gymnast-gears-up-for-spin-in-paris\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  PublishedJun 14, 2024, 04:46 PM  UpdatedJun 14, 2024, 04:46 PM  JAKARTA - It was hours after being admitted to a hospital in Belgium following a sharp landing from the uneven bars that Rifda Irfanaluthfi learned she had become the first Indonesian gymnast to qualify for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.206737473533097e-20, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Billie_Jean_King_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.7497321816557992, \"rank\": 0.331241785707904, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Billie_Jean_King_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Billie_Jean_King_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rifda_Irfanaluthfi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rifda Irfanaluthfi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rifda_Irfanaluthfi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rifda_Irfanaluthfi\"}, {\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 0.558606186779256, \"rank\": 0.7901699280835237, \"text\": \"Indonesian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the back of an ambulance, the 24-year-old had been furiously firing off messages.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kept asking my manager, my coach and my friends.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I texted them one by one to ask: Did I qualify?\\\"\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she recalled.\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The morning after sustaining the injury Rifda received the news that she needed knee surgery.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also learned that she had qualified for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the time I was crying, hugging my coach,\\\" she said after a training session in Jakarta.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.0728607345820947e-11, \"text\": \"Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My coach told me that finally our struggle from 2015 had become a reality.\\\"\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Almost two years after her surgery and hours upon hours of dogged daily practice, Rifda is readying herself for Paris where she will compete in artistic gymnastics, which includes a number of individual competitions on different apparatus such as the beam, vault and uneven bars.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999935807864, \"rank\": 6.419221961062577e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indonesia, which is hoping to send about 20 athletes to Paris, has won 37 medals at the Olympics - 36 of them coming from badminton and weightlifting, with a solitary silver in archery.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9998005050144723, \"rank\": 0.00013767281130967624, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}, {\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999935807864, \"rank\": 6.419221961062577e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rifda hopes her Olympic debut will help raise the profile of a sport often overlooked in the Southeast Asian nation.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"score\": 0.9999999982510417, \"rank\": 1.251225579669171e-09, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She jokes that knowledge about gymnastics in Indonesia is so limited that some people still think she does aerobics.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9998005050144723, \"rank\": 0.00013767281130967624, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rifda's longtime coach and former professional gymnast Eva Butar-Butar says the athlete's participation in Paris would be a \\\"groundbreaking moment for the sport in Indonesia\\\".\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1864, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999935807864, \"rank\": 6.419221961062577e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9998005050144723, \"rank\": 0.00013767281130967624, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not because we do not have the athletes,\\\" said Butar-Butar.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But more because of the support system that makes it difficult for Indonesian athletes to reach a global level.\\\"\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 0.558606186779256, \"rank\": 0.7901699280835237, \"text\": \"Indonesian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ranked 52nd in the world, Rifda had long aspired to be a professional athlete, switching from swimming to gymnastics by age six and winning a stack of prizes.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pictures of Rifda as a child posted on her Instagram show her father helping her do handstand push-ups.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2318, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.567995301242829e-28, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rifda fondly recalls going jogging around a park every weekend with her parents, whose support, she says, has been central to her success.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BULLIED ONLINE  The walls of Rifda's childhood home in South Jakarta are adorned with her trophies, awards and the latest addition - a framed magazine cover featuring a portrait of Rifda and the headline: \\\"Made it to the Paris 2024 Olympics!\\\"\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"score\": 0.9999999998394742, \"rank\": 1.6062653083876579e-10, \"text\": \"South Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\"}, {\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rifda's mother Yulies Andriana, who formerly worked as a teacher at a specialist sports school, said her daughter had fought through many challenges as a young athlete.\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andriana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andriana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andriana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andriana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not afford expensive training and gymnastics clothes, so we always had to thrift for second-hand clothes,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was sad, but it was all I could do.\\\"\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These days, she said, her daughter has been facing a different challenge.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the world's most populous Muslim-majority nation, religious conservatives have recently harassed Rifda online, describing photos of her in leotards as \\\"pornographic\\\".\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was bullied online,\\\" said her mother.\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So she had to shut down the comments to stop it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the lead-up to Paris, where she will compete next to her idol, American gymnast Simone Biles, Rifda spends much of her days at a run-down gymnasium in East Jakarta, perfecting her backflips, spins and routine on an aged balance beam, alongside some tattered mats.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3460, \"end\": 3465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999935807864, \"rank\": 6.419221961062577e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3508, \"end\": 3516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999959430570455, \"rank\": 2.909670890459392e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 3596, \"end\": 3608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Jakarta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"East Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Jakarta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Counting down the weeks, Rifda admits she is nervous but hopes that no matter what happens her performance will inspire other young Indonesian athletes.\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3842, \"end\": 3852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 0.558606186779256, \"rank\": 0.7901699280835237, \"text\": \"Indonesian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is not for me alone.\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to motivate everyone, especially young athletes, not only for artistic gymnastics, but in other sports as well that have never qualified for the Olympics,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 4063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to tell them if I can do it, then you can too.\\\"\", \"from\": 4065, \"to\": 4120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS  Surgery  Gymnastics  Belgium  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4275, \"entities\": 